import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    avg_yield = data.groupby('variety')['yield'].mean().reset_index()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='variety', y='yield', data=avg_yield)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        chart.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title("What is the average yield of each variety across all sites and years?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
